node.text: the official music video for Don’t Freak Out is out NOW ! this was truly one of the most insane and fun days I’ve ever had, and a big shout out to @ianndior, @tysonritter, @travisbarker and the whole creative team for making this video come to life

node.text:
and finally, my third and final announcement this week… my debut album “Teenage Heartbreak” is out SEPTEMBER 17TH
words can’t even describe how excited I am to share this fucking masterpiece with the world i have never been this proud of an accomplishment of mine before and i know y’all will be proud too. my new song from the album Don’t Freak Out feat. @ianndior, @tysonritter, and @travisbarker is out rn go stream! the official music video is out tomorrow at 9am pt LETS RAGGGEEEE
